:"2019-12-30T12:41:40.000Z","msg":"巴打有冇可能帶埋女朋友去？<br />\n定係佢肯等你？<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T01:11:25.000Z","msg":"未同佢講，因為我自己都未揸定主意<br />\n不過佢係啲離唔開香港嘅人 之前試探過佢，問佢有冇興趣去wh，佢好快速咁話冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我諗都要long D一段時間。"},{"pid":"2b9d839c9d80561b2e2c2a33b4f0c38cf190c58c","tid":1802840,"uid":49944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T01:58:47.000Z","msg":"有咩放唔低<br />\n定期Whatsapp 見面咪得囉"},{"pid":"4641f01e3e4b42d0ba1bc78630efb42d84d61ad5","tid":1802840,"uid":42350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T02:07:27.000Z","msg":"走la <img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咪再返來"},{"pid":"357d89e384e7e6886a81dcea650685abfa49c257","tid":1802840,"uid":276715,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T03:23:05.000Z","msg":"決定左就唔好諗喇<br />\n你移日本有咩事4個鐘就飛到返香港啦<br />\n要見嘅一年都見到幾次面 其實唔係諗到咁差<br />\n我係歐洲想見一面洗成皮野再加成日飛機<br />\n我都諗過係咪好不孝<br />\n但人生屬於自己 走自己嘅路先對得住自己"},{"pid":"1dae69880fb978aa0ecee21fda4e397d8fb6a796","tid":1802840,"uid":127554,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T15:07:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我調返轉<br />\n全家移左民去外國<br />\n但最後我都係返咗嚟香港<br />\n因為香港永遠都係屋企<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c117f289ec30dcd0a2eb2979128bee3d3e0ea24a","tid":1802840,"uid":138304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T16:46:26.000Z","msg":"我都有諗過移日本<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />絲打覺得嗰邊好唔好生活？"},{"pid":"46b3226b99f754b9a29034643e1c931d2e663ea1","tid":1802840,"uid":130060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1dae69880fb978aa0ecee21fda4e397d8fb6a796","tid":1802840,"uid":127554,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T15:07:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/heard.gif\" c